Create Project:
cds init --add nodejs incident-management

To Create SAP Fiori App:
Command Platter(Ctrl+Shift+P) -> Fiori: Open Application Generator -> List Report Page -> Use ocal Cap Project, choose other ->

Run SAP Fiori:
Command Platter(Ctrl+Shift+P) -> Fiori: Open Application Info -> Preview Application -> npm run watch-incidents(second one)

SAP Fiori Launch page:
To launch Preview Application
https://port4004-workspaces-ws-9pkk5.us10.trial.applicationstudio.cloud.sap/launchpage.html#Shell-home

Add tests dependencies:
npm add -D @cap-js/cds-test
